  title="MAX98357A I2S Amplifier with ESP32"
  description="How to play audio on an ESP32 Dev Board using a MAX98357A I2S amplifier. Covers wiring, I2S setup, audio prep, WAV-to-header conversion, and the full Arduino sketch."
